<p>Amendment by <a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._108-458">Pub. L. 108–458</a> effective not later than six months after <span class="date" date="2004-12-17">Dec. 17, 2004</span>, except as otherwise expressly provided, see <a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._108-458">section 1097(a) of Pub. L. 108–458</a>, set out in an Effective Date of 2004 Amendment; Transition Provisions note under <a href="/uscode/text/50/3001">section 3001 of this title</a>.</p>
</div>
